						<div class="postbody">Under the assumption that you want fully detailed platforms like those of certain parts of <em>Bucky O'Hare</em>:<br /><br />4. MMC3 using the forthcoming INL-ROM mini. Or were you aiming to get your work onto a collaborative multicart that lacks a scanline counter?<br /><br />5. Spend most of the CPU time in a cycle waiting loop. This is doable and has been used in games like F-1 Race and Rad Racer. Possibly letterbox the display to give time at the top and bottom of the screen for game processing.</div>

